V0604_01_00_00_0.text:
Hello everyone!
Ready for a great time?

V0604_01_00_01_0.text:
Hey you!
That's right - you!
Get ready for a great show!

V0604_01_00_01_1.text: I'll win this Duel for the best fans in the world!

V0604_01_00_02_0.text:
Okay, everybody!
The Duel's about to begin!

V0604_01_00_03_0.text: You'll learn what my Trickstars can do!

V0604_01_00_04_0.text:
Sure!
I'll let you check out my Trickstar Deck!

V0604_01_00_05_0.text:
Sorry to keep you waiting!
I'll make up for it in this Duel!

V0604_01_00_06_0.text:
Let's Duel, Playmaker!
I'll win this time!

V0604_01_00_07_0.text: You'll be feeling blue after I'm through with you!

V0604_01_00_08_0.text:
Spectre...
I'm gonna defeat you - and that's no fairy tale!

V0604_01_00_09_0.text: Let's see why my brother thinks so highly of you, Ghost Gal!

V0604_01_00_10_0.text:
Akira...
I'll prove to you that I can fend for myself!

V0604_03_00_00_0.text: I have everything I need to win!

V0604_03_00_01_0.text: You're not going to get another turn!

V0604_03_00_05_0.text:
It's not over yet!
This is when my Trickstars get in gear!

V0604_05_00_00_0.text:
This draw will decide everything.
But I believe in my deck!

V0604_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0604_11_01_00_0.text: I'll Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0604_11_10_01_0.text: I’ll build the circuit that turns dreams into reality!

V0604_11_10_02_0.text: I’ll build the circuit that turns dreams into reality!

V0604_11_10_02_1.text:
I set my monsters in the Link Arrows!
Link the circuit!

V0604_16_00_01_0.text: This is gonna be the final battle!

V0604_21_00_00_0.text: My Trickstars have many more tricks in store!

V0604_21_00_01_0.text:
C'mon! I know you're better than this!
Let's have fun!

V0604_21_00_03_0.text: I'm going to end my turn!

V0604_21_00_05_0.text:
The Duel isn't over yet!
I can turn this around!

V0604_28_00_00_0.text:
That's the end of the show!
Until next time - stay blue!

V0604_28_00_02_0.text: When people are counting on you, that's a lot of pressure.

V0604_28_00_02_1.text: That's why I fight hard so I won't let them down!

V0604_28_00_03_0.text:
That was only an appetizer.
My Trickstars can dish out more!

V0604_28_00_04_0.text:
Sorry!
If you wanna chalk it up to bad luck, go ahead!

V0604_28_00_05_0.text:
I'll put you on the right path.
Like a true angel.

V0604_28_00_06_0.text: I get stronger everyday so I can fight for my friends!

V0604_28_00_07_1.text:
For my friends.
And for you!

V0604_28_00_09_0.text:
I refuse to lose!
Because losing means I lose everything!

V0604_29_00_00_0.text:
Argh!
How could it end like this?

V0604_29_00_01_0.text:
Sorry fans!
I couldn't bring home the victory.

V0604_29_00_01_1.text:
But I'll win next time!
Just for you!

V0604_29_00_03_0.text: The next Duel won't end the same - and that's a promise!

V0604_29_00_04_0.text: The hard part about fame is that everyone knows your moves.

V0604_29_00_05_0.text: You hit my deck's weakness before I could chip you down.

V0604_29_00_06_0.text: Does messing with my mind make you happy!?

V0604_29_00_07_0.text: You're not just a great hacker, you're a great Duelist!

V0604_29_00_09_0.text:
You're tough...
And I don't think you were even trying...

V0604_33_00_01_0.text: I'm going to use this Skill!

V0604_33_00_02_0.text: Now's the time for my Skill!

V0604_33_00_04_0.text:
I activate my Skill!
Trickstar Trick!

V0604_33_00_05_0.text:
I activate my Skill!
Trickstar Gig!

V0604_33_00_06_0.text:
I activate my Skill!
Shape of Sea!

V0604_30_00_01_0.text: You think you can deal more effect damage than me?

V0604_30_00_02_0.text: If it comes down to effect damage, I'm gonna win!

V0604_34_00_00_0.text: When I'm upset, you best stay outta my way!

V0604_34_00_04_0.text: Just another reason why I gotta take you down!

V0604_34_00_06_0.text: I think I know how your deck works!

V0604_34_00_08_0.text: It's not too late to change! I'll put you on the right path!

V0604_34_00_09_0.text: Blue Angel is here to save you!

V0604_32_00_01_0.text:
Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Links!
It's time to link into the VRAINS!

V0604_36_00_02_0.text: My bad! But you got this!

V0604_36_00_08_0.text: Ack... I hope you have better moves than me, Ghost Gal!

V0604_08_00_00_0.text:
I'll activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Trickstar Bouquet!

I activate my Field Spell!
Trickstar Light Arena!

V0604_08_00_03_0.text:
I activate my Field Spell!
Trickstar Light Stage!

V0604_08_00_04_0.text: I activate Trickstar Light Stage's effect!

V0604_08_00_05_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Trickstar Festival!

V0604_08_00_06_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Trickstar Fusion!

V0604_08_00_07_0.text: I banish Trickstar Fusion from my Grave to use its effect!

V0604_08_00_08_0.text: I activate the Equip Spell, Trickstar Magical Laurel!

V0604_08_00_10_0.text: I activate the Field Spell, Trickstar Live Stage!

V0604_08_00_12_0.text:
I activate my Trap Card!
Trickstar Reincarnation!

V0604_08_00_13_0.text: I banish Trickstar Reincarnation from my Graveyard!

V0604_08_00_14_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Angel of Blue Tears!

V0604_08_00_15_0.text: I banish Angel of Blue Tears from my Grave to activate it!

V0604_08_00_16_0.text:
I activate my Field Spell!
Marincess Battle Ocean!

V0604_08_00_18_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Marincess Dive!

V0604_08_00_19_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Marincess Snow!

V0604_08_00_20_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Marincess Current!

V0604_08_00_21_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Marincess Circulation!

V0604_08_00_22_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Marincess Wave!

V0604_08_00_23_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Marincess Cascade!

V0604_08_00_24_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Marincess Bubble Ring!

V0604_08_00_25_0.text: I banish Bubble Ring from my Graveyard to use its effect!

V0604_09_00_12_0.text: I activate Trickstar Lycoris's effect from my hand!

V0604_09_00_13_0.text: Trickstar Mandrake went from my hand to the Graveyard!

V0604_09_00_14_0.text: Mandrake was used to Link Summon, so her effect activates!

V0604_09_00_15_0.text: My Lilybell's effect activates when she's added to my hand!

V0604_09_00_18_0.text: I activate Trickstar Corobane's effect from my hand!

V0604_09_00_20_0.text:
From my hand...
Dark Angel activates her effect!

V0604_09_00_23_0.text: By banishing a monster, Bubble Reef lets me draw a card!

V0604_09_00_24_0.text: Since a monster was banished, Great Bubble Reef gains ATK!

V0604_09_00_25_0.text: Bubble Reef sends a Water monster from my hand to the Grave!

V0604_09_00_28_0.text: I banish Coral Triangle from my Graveyard to use her effect!

V0604_09_00_29_0.text: My Sea Angel can use her effect when she's Link Summoned!

V0604_09_00_30_0.text: When Blue Slug is Link Summoned, she can use her effect!

V0604_09_00_32_0.text: I activate Marincess Wonder Heart's effect!

V0604_09_00_33_0.text: I activate Marincess Crown Tail's effect from my hand!

V0604_09_00_34_0.text: Marincess Crown Tail's effect activates from the Graveyard!

V0604_09_00_35_0.text: I send Marincess Sea Star from my hand to the Graveyard!

V0604_09_00_36_0.text: I banish my Sea Horse from my Graveyard to use her effect!

V0604_09_00_37_0.text: I activate Marincess Sleepy Maiden's effect from my hand!

V0604_09_00_38_0.text: I banish Sleepy Maiden from my Graveyard to use her effect!

V0604_09_00_42_0.text: Blue Tang was used to Link Summon, so her effect activates!

V0604_09_00_44_0.text: I activate Marincess Springirl's effect from my hand!

V0604_09_00_45_0.text: Springirl was used to Link Summon, so her effect activates!

V0604_09_00_46_0.text: Summoning Marincess Pascalus activates her effect!

V0604_09_00_47_0.text: I banish Pascalus from my Graveyard to activate her effect!

Come on out!
Link 2 Trickstar Black Catbat!

Dark Angel!

Bubble up!

Let's do this!

Swim on in!

This is perfect!

Show yourself!
